songs.title: Get Back (Live)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: Demi Lovato]
Put your hands together!

[Verse 1: Demi Lovato]
Don't walk away like you always do, this time
Baby, you're the only thing that's been on my mind
Ever since you left, I've been a mess
You won't answer your phone
I'll say it once, and I'll leave you alone, but I gotta let you know

[Chorus: Demi Lovato]
I wanna get back to the old days
When the phone would ring and I knew it was you
I wanna talk back and get yelled at
Fight for nothing, like we used to
Oh, kiss me like you mean it, like you miss me
Cause I know that you do
I wanna get back, get back with you

[Verse 2: Demi Lovato]
Don't look at me that way, I see it in your eyes
Don't worry about me, I've been fine
I'm not gonna lie, I've been a mess since you've left
And every time I see you, it gets more and more intense

[Chorus: Demi Lovato]
I wanna get back to the old days
When the phone would ring and I knew it was you
I wanna talk back and get yelled at
Fight for nothing, like we used to
Oh, kiss me like you mean it, like you miss me
Cause I know that you do
I wanna get back, get back with you

[Bridge: Demi Lovato]
You were the only one I wanted
You were the first one I fell for
You're the only one that I'm in need of
And I don't want to be lonely anymore

[Chorus: Demi Lovato]
I wanna get back to the old days
When the phone would ring and I knew it was you
I wanna talk back and get yelled at
Fight for nothing, like we used to
Oh, kiss me like you mean it, like you miss me
Cause I know that you do
I wanna get back, get back with you

[Breakdown: Demi Lovato]
(Get back!) Get Back!
C'mon, sing it!
(Get back!) Get Back!
(Get back!) Get Back!
(Get back!) Get Back!

[Chorus - Shortened: Demi Lovato]
Oh, kiss me like you mean it, like you miss me
Cause I know that you do

[Outro: Demi Lovato]
I wanna get back, get back
I wanna get back, get back
I wanna get back, get back with you
Get back, yeah!

[Talking: Demi Lovato]
Thank you so much!
I love you too!
Thank you guys so much!
It's so sweet!
I love you guys so much!
Give it up for my band!
Thank you!
